Hi Everyone,

Following steering conversations on funding the BIDS project(s), we had a
quick chat with Yarik. We plan to submit an LOI for TIER2 to this call
<https://os4science.org/funding_opportunity/os4ls/> for the BIDS community.
One idea is to develop the BIDS community towards standardization of
"bids-study", enabling agentic AI to do a whole neuroimaging study and
"biomarker discovery ready". I am sure other ideas will emerge :)

The call is going to be super competitive, we expect many to apply.

Let us know what you think, and I would like to dedicate a steering meeting
to this before OHBM if possible.

Cheers
JB

